gov.usgs.earthquake.nshmp.data

Interface XyPoint


  • public interface XyPoint
    Wrapper interface for xy-value data pairs. Implementations that permit setting the y-value will propogate through to any backing data structure (e.g. a XySequence).
    Author:
    Peter Powers
    See Also:
    XySequence
